ducation and sociolinguistics.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aBilingualism. 0aSocialization. 0aSociolinguistics. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / Sociolinguistics.2bisacsh  abilingualism.  alanguage socialization.  amultilingualism.  asociolinguistics.1 aAtkinson, Dwight, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBayley, Robert, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBayley, Robert, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aBell, Jill Sinclair, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCole, Kimmarie, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGoldstein, Tara, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHarklau, Linda, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHe, Agnes Weiyun, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKhayatt, Didi, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLamarre, Patricia, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLangman, Juliet, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLotherington, Heather, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLuykx, Aurolyn, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMcall, Christopher, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPatrick, Donna, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPease-Alvarez, Lucinda, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPiedra, María De La, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPon, Gordon, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRomo, Harriett D., econt